summary_one_paragraph: This U.K. Liaison file references cables LOND 5956 (IN 27353) from March 29, 1961, and LOND 5963 (IN 28181) from March 31, 1961. It contains extra sensitive cables that are restricted, indicating they should only be opened by the Chief of WH/A/PA, suggesting a high level of confidentiality and sensitivity within the contents.
